534
00:38:46,337 --> 00:38:47,018
Why?

535
00:38:48,769 --> 00:38:49,717
Cause it’s fun.

536
00:38:51,684 --> 00:38:52,697
Don’t you remember?

537
00:39:05,015 --> 00:39:07,699
Alright Ladies and gentlemen, give it up for Gavin DeGraw!

538
00:39:12,061 --> 00:39:17,864
I don't need to be anything other than a prison guard's son

539
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:23,807
I don't need to be anything other than a specialist's son

540
00:39:24,482 --> 00:39:30,360
I don't have to be anyone other than a birth of two souls in one

541
00:39:30,728 --> 00:39:36,355
Part of where I'm going is knowing where I'm coming from

542
00:39:36,448 --> 00:39:42,517
I don't want to be anything other than what I've been trying to be lately

543
00:39:42,613 --> 00:39:48,009
All I have to do is think of me and I have peace of mind

544
00:39:48,736 --> 00:39:52,510
I'm tired of looking 'round rooms wondering what I gotta do

545
00:39:52,592 --> 00:39:54,947
Or who I'm supposed to be

546
00:39:55,064 --> 00:39:59,826
I don't want to be anything other than me

