00:40:05,903 --> 00:40:09,253
I’m Mouth McFadden and tonight this is the only game that matters.

549
00:40:23,476 --> 00:40:24,167
Hey.

550
00:40:24,716 --> 00:40:25,888
Hey, tutor girl!

551
00:40:45,093 --> 00:40:47,264
I guess this answers the gay question.

552
00:40:49,395 --> 00:40:50,264
Give me this.

553
00:40:52,117 --> 00:40:53,007
Get in.

554
00:40:56,136 --> 00:40:57,089
Cheese!

555
00:41:06,519 --> 00:41:08,286
I thought you might want to see this, coach.

556
00:41:10,574 --> 00:41:13,053
Come a long way since the last time we sat here.

557
00:41:14,018 --> 00:41:19,745
Uh huh. Makes you wonder where they’re all headed.

558
00:41:36,252 --> 00:41:37,009
Busy night?

559
00:41:38,858 --> 00:41:40,077
What happened today, Dan?

560
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:44,449
Oh you know, we were going to spend the weekend but we missed you too much.

561
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:48,248
I ask you to make good with your son and you make it worse.

562
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:52,101
He flipped out on the 18th hole. It was embarrassing.

563
00:41:52,498 --> 00:41:54,685
And did you badger him into it?

564
00:41:59,202 --> 00:42:01,329
You have a problem, Dan.

565
00:42:01,510 --> 00:42:04,524
