571
00:42:21,155 --> 00:42:22,464
I want you to see someone.

572
00:42:23,152 --> 00:42:25,645
A therapist. We’ll go as a family.

573
00:42:26,055 --> 00:42:26,803
Forget it.

574
00:42:27,425 --> 00:42:29,809
It's not a negotiation, Dan.

575
00:42:30,208 --> 00:42:32,690
You get some help or you’re not going to see Nathan.

